DOCUMENT();        # This should be the first executable line in the problem.

loadMacros('PGstandard.pl', 'PGML.pl', 'PGcourse.pl');

$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

Context("Numeric");

$a1 = Real(random(1,9,1));
$a1sq=$a1*$a1;
$b1 = 2*$a1;
$c1 = random(1,200,1);
$d1 = $c1-$a1sq;

BEGIN_PGML

Complete the square. 

    [``x^2+[$b1] x +[$c1]``]=[``\Big(x+``][_]{$a1}{20}[``\Big)^2+\ ``][_]{$d1}{20}

END_PGML

BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION
In the polynomial [``x^2+[$b1] x +[$c1]``] the coefficient of [`x`] is [$b1].  Also [``[$b1]=2([$a1])``].  Thus 

    [``(x+[$a1])^2=x^2+[$b1]x+[$a1sq]``],
    
and

    [`` \Big(x+[$a1]\Big)^2-[$a1sq]=x^2+[$b1]x ``].

so 
    [``x^2+[$b1] x +[$c1]=\Big(x+[$a1]\Big)^2-[$a1sq]+[$c1]=\Big(x+[$a1]\Big)^2+([$d1])``]
END_PGML_SOLUTION
ENDDOCUMENT();        # This should be the last executable line in the problem.